Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.87,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「警告 紧急情况」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:24.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,结界！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:33.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔力反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,找到大鱼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,上阵吧 钢铁伯爵
