Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.68,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Standby ready{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.67,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Set Up{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.48,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H81111EE&)}Schwalbefliegen{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}云燕翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:28.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,为什么突然袭击我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,你是哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,为什么这样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:38.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,至少告诉我理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,你这丫头！
