Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H81111EE&}──飞槌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.63,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H88000BB&)}Protection{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}防御
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,砸穿它！
