Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:54.91,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「明白」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:54.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,就这样结束了吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:56.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤诺君…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:22:58.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺君…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:00.37,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:13.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,对不起 奈叶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:14.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:17.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤诺… 君…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:18.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,是同伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:25.69,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Scythe Form{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光镰形态
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:30.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,──是朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.39,0:25:11.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,开端总是如此陡然
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.58,0:25:14.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,但是 面对这过分陡然的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.88,0:25:16.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,混乱… 困惑…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:17.61,Default1,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.12,0:25:20.31,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们在强敌面前陷入绝境
